import React from "react";
import {
  Container,
  Row,
  Col,
  Card,
  Form
} from "react-bootstrap";

function User() {
  return (
    <>
      <Container fluid>
        <Row>
          <Col md="8">
            
            <Card>
              <Card.Header>
                <Card.Title as="h3">Edit Profile</Card.Title>
              </Card.Header>

              <Card.Body>
                <Form>
                  <Row> 
                    <Col md="6"> 
                    <Form.Group>
                        <label> School </label>
                        <Form.Control
                          defaultValue="Badger Primary School"
                          
                          placeholder="Company"
                          type="text"
                        ></Form.Control>
                      </Form.Group>
                    </Col>
                  </Row>

                </Form>


              </Card.Body>

            </Card>

          </Col>
        </Row>
      </Container>
    </>
  );
}
export default User;
